Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.62,0:47:21.87,Začátek,,0,0,0,,O 5 let později
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.87,0:47:22.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.02,0:47:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Promiňte.
